# Privacy Policy for Quick Sudoku

Last Updated: 2025-11-13

Thank you for using Quick Sudoku ("we," "us," or "our"). This Privacy Policy is meant to help you understand what information we collect, why we collect it, and how you can manage it.
Your privacy is important to us. It is our policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect from you across our application, Quick Sudoku.

## 1. Information We Collect

We do not collect any personally identifiable information from you when you use our application. The application is designed to be used without requiring you to provide any personal data such as your name, email address, or location.

## 2. How We Use Your Information

Since we do not collect any personal information, we do not use it for any purpose.

## 3. Data Storage on Your Device

The Quick Sudoku application may save its internal state directly on your device. This data is stored locally and is not transmitted to us or any third party. This stored data may include:

- Game progress (e.g., current Sudoku puzzles, saved games)
- User preferences and settings (e.g., theme, difficulty level)

This information is stored solely for the purpose of providing you with a seamless and personalized application experience. You have control over this data, and it can typically be cleared by uninstalling the application or clearing the application's data through your device's settings.

## 4. Third-Party Services

Our application does not integrate with any third-party services that would collect information from you.
We are currently not using any ads provider.

## 5. Children's Privacy

We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. Since the application does not collect any personal data, it is safe for use by all ages.

## 6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy within the application or on our website. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

## 7. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Google Play Developer Account: GummyBear Studio
Application Name: com.gummybearstudio.quicksudoku

